  color, typography, spacing, form elements, and overall visual interest. The
  approach involved a comprehensive overhaul, starting with a new calming,
  sleep-themed color palette. This was followed by significant updates to the
  main  layout, including decorative background elements, a
  redesigned progress indicator, and a subtle star pattern on card headers. The
   was transformed with a hero element and feature cards, and all
  core UI components like checkboxes, radio buttons, sliders, and progress bars
  received a polished, consistent look. Crucially, all 14 form sections were
  refactored to use the new card-style groupings and theme colors, moving away
  from the previous plain gray boxes. The  also received a visual
  refresh with consistent card headers and improved content styling. The changes
  aimed to create a more professional, calming, and engaging user experience.
